readme:
# bzip2

Buckaroo package for bzip2. 

Extracted from https://www.sourceware.org/bzip2/#bzip2-latest at version `1.0.2`. 

[![Travis (.org)](https://img.shields.io/travis/buckaroo-pm/bzip2.svg)](https://travis-ci.org/buckaroo-pm/bzip2) [![AppVeyor](https://img.shields.io/appveyor/ci/njlr/bzip2.svg)](https://ci.appveyor.com/project/njlr/bzip2)

versions.buck:
cxx_library(
  name = 'bzip2', 
  header_namespace = '', 
  exported_headers = [
    'bzlib.h', 
  ], 
  headers = glob([
    '*.h', 
  ]), 
  srcs = [
    'blocksort.c', 
    'huffman.c', 
    'crctable.c', 
    'randtable.c', 
    'compress.c', 
    'decompress.c', 
    'bzlib.c', 
  ], 
  visibility = [
    'PUBLIC', 
  ], 
)

cxx_binary(
  name = 'bzip2-tool', 
  srcs = [
    'bzip2.c', 
  ], 
  deps = [
    ':bzip2', 
  ], 
)

cxx_binary(
  name = 'dlltest', 
  srcs = [
    'dlltest.c', 
  ], 
  deps = [
    ':bzip2', 
  ], 
)

cxx_binary(
  name = 'mk251', 
  srcs = [
    'mk251.c', 
  ], 
  deps = [
    ':bzip2', 
  ], 
)

cxx_binary(
  name = 'unzcrash', 
  srcs = [
    'unzcrash.c', 
  ], 
  deps = [
    ':bzip2', 
  ], 
)
